{"tid":2177259,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"變 製作成本入不敷出？ Netflix 科幻影集《碳變》播出兩季後宣告腰斬！","createTime":"2020-08-27T14:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:31:14.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ac98bc951c3c5e4bcef42e09722138b9836e46c7","tid":2177259,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=9827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D9827&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONuEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=84127c48\" target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=9827</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5266f6496f5a4c1074cf586dfcef1cf01555ffbf","tid":2177259,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159849341345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159849341345.jpg&h=1d16cc6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetfilx宣布不再續訂影集《碳變》（Altered Carbon），這意味著《碳變》在第二季後宣告完結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/15984934236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F15984934236.jpg&h=22bc64f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由安東尼&middot;麥基（Anthony Mackie）主演的《碳變》第二季於2月27日上映，隨後於3月19日發行了動畫電影。<br />\n<br />\n據相關人士透露Netflix決定不續訂此影集的決定是在4月做出的，此決策與新冠肺炎疫情沒有關係，而是基於串流媒體的收視率與製作成本來擬定的。（Netflix最近基於疫情取消了兩部之前續訂的影集《新社會》（The Society）和《這樣不OK》 （I Am Not Okay with This）<br />\n<br />\n《碳變》改編自自英國作家理察&middot;K&middot;摩根在2002年發行的同名小說。描述在一個意識可以轉移到不同軀體的世界，一位前菁英士兵武&middot;科瓦奇轉變成私家偵探，他被委託調查一位富商的謀殺案的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159849370156.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159849370156.jpeg&h=60107ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《碳變》第二季的舞台為第一季結尾的後30年，安東尼&middot;麥基飾演的武&middot;科瓦奇為精英星際戰士中唯一倖存的戰士，他繼續他持續了數百年的探索行動，為的是尋找失去的摯愛奎爾克里斯特&middot;法肯納（蕾妮‧伊莉‧高德斯伯瑞／Ren&eacute;e Elise Goldsberry飾演）。<br />\n<br />\n在第二季中安東尼&middot;麥基接下了由喬爾&middot;金納曼（Joel Kinnaman）飾演的武&middot;科瓦奇。第一季的製作人約翰&middot;G&middot;勒尼奇（John G. Lenic）在第二季開拍前也離開劇組，改為艾莉森&middot;沙珀克（Alison Schenker）擔任第二季的製作人。<br />\n<br />\n這部賽博龐克類型的影集在推出時被視為美劇的一大創舉，可能就是製作成本太高再加上第二季評價比不上第一季所以才被腰斬，有這麼好的題材卻沒發揮出來實在可惜！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2020/08/altered-carbon-canceled-netflix-after-2-seasons-1203023456/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2020%2F08%2Faltered-carbon-canceled-netflix-after-2-seasons-1203023456%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONuEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=40877a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2020/08/altered-carbon-canceled-netflix-after-2-seasons-1203023456/</a>"},{"pid":"05eb70bbbbe69c9dea3b8d4ded71c15ed7d480ec","tid":2177259,"uid":168911,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"其實睇S2一路睇一路覺得 製作真係幾落本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界觀好正，劇情一般，但有S3既話我都會繼續追<br />\n<br />\n最大問題男女主角都唔同哂，個投入感真係太減"},{"pid":"05cde817c87e63c9d534b05af929ec782b336a59","tid":2177259,"uid":28114,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"q